sequenceDiagram
    participant Gateway as Envoy/Gateway
    participant ExtAuthz as ext-authz (SidecarRouteHandler)
    participant AuthCore as auth-core (AuthorizationUseCase)
    participant RolesSvc as Roles Service (via ext-authz Client)
    participant OpaWasm as opa-wasm (PolicyEngine)

    Note over Gateway,OpaWasm: Request Flow (Sequence)
    
    Gateway->>ExtAuthz: 1. GET /authorize (Tokens & Headers)
    
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
    Note over ExtAuthz: 2. HeaderSanitizer prüft Inputs
    ExtAuthz->>AuthCore: 2. Async Call (validate/authorize)
    end
    
    rect rgb(230, 245, 230)
    Note over AuthCore: 3. Extrahiert Claims aus Token
    AuthCore->>RolesSvc: 3. Hole externe Rollen
    RolesSvc-->>AuthCore: 3. Return User Roles
    Note over AuthCore: 3. Bündelt Daten in AuthContext
    end
    
    rect rgb(245, 230, 230)
    AuthCore->>OpaWasm: 4. Evaluierung anfragen (AuthContext)
    Note over OpaWasm: 5. AuthContext -> JSON
    Note over OpaWasm: 5. Führt WASM-Policy aus
    OpaWasm-->>AuthCore: 5. Return PolicyDecision (Allow/Deny)
    end
    
    AuthCore-->>ExtAuthz: Return ProcessingResult
    
    alt Allowed
        ExtAuthz-->>Gateway: 6. 200 OK (inkl. X-Auth-User-Id, X-Enriched-Roles)
    else Denied
        ExtAuthz-->>Gateway: 6. 401/403 (Unauthorized/Forbidden)
    end
